events.title: Beast Graphic card series NVIDIA
events.description: The latest NVIDIA graphics cards are the GeForce RTX 50 series, which succeeded the 40 series and launched in early 2025 with models like the RTX 5080 and RTX 5090. These new cards are powered by the Blackwell architecture and feature enhanced AI capabilities, DLSS 4 with multi-frame generation, and GDDR7 memory.

events.title: Gaming industry in india
events.description: There are over 400 gaming organisations in India, which is the home to around 420 million online gamers. The gaming industry at present registers a growth rate of 38%. By the year 2025, the gaming industry in India is anticipated to reach $3.9 billion in value.
